RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT MODULE_ID, MODULE_DESC FROM(SELECT MODULE_ID,MODULE_DESC FROM OLVWS_MODULES WHERE RECORD_STAT='O' AND AUTH_STAT='A' UNION SELECT 'AL','ALL MODULES' FROM DUAL) WHERE 1=1 ORDER BY MODULE_ID
SELECT CCY_CODE,CCY_NAME FROM CYTMS_CCY_DEFN WHERE ONCE_AUTH = 'Y' AND RECORD_STAT = 'O' ORDER BY CCY_CODE

SELECT PRODUCT_CODE,PRODUCT_DESCRIPTION FROM(SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_CODE,PRODUCT_DESCRIPTION FROM OLTMS_PRODUCT WHERE MODULE = ? AND AUTH_STAT ='A' AND RECORD_STAT ='O' UNION SELECT 'ALL','ALL PRODUCTS' FROM DUAL) WHERE 1 = 1 ORDER BY PRODUCT_CODE
SELECT SOURCE_CODE FROM COTM_SOURCE WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A'
SELECT DISTINCT ROLE_ID,ROLE_DESCRIPTION FROM SMTB_ROLE_MASTER WHERE ONCE_AUTH = 'Y' AND RECORD_STAT = 'O'
